r if the application uses\n  the SYS or other default account and SYSTEM tablespace to store its objects,\n  this is a finding.","fix_text":"Create and assign dedicated tablespaces for the storage of data\n  by each application using the CREATE TABLESPACE command.","impact":"0.5","profile_name":"Oracle Database 12c Security Technical Implementation Guide","profile_shasum":"6a8047b6a1ee06ffa684da2fa3b403e8d8b033d344ad79aa36b9aa9c04228338","status":["failed","failed","failed","failed","failed","failed","failed","failed","failed","failed","failed","failed","failed","failed"],"message":["FAILED -- Test: oracle db application owners: MDSYS should be in \"a\" and \"b\"\nMessage: expected `MDSYS` to be in the list: `[\"a\", \"b\"]`\n","FAILED -- Test: oracle db application owners: OUTLN should be in \"a\" and \"b\"\nMessage: expected `OUTLN` to be in the list: `[\"a\", \"b\"]`\n","FAILED -- Test: oracle db application owners: CTXSYS should be in \"a\" and \"b\"\nMessage: expected `CTXSYS` to be in the list: `[\"a\", \"b\"]`\n","FAILED -- Test: oracle db application owners: SYSTEM should be in \"a\" and \"b\"\nMessage: expected `SYSTEM` to be in the list: `[\"a\", \"b\"]`\n","FAILED -- Test: oracle db application owners: DVSYS should be in \"a\" and \"b\"\nMessage: expected `DVSYS` to be in the list: `[\"a\", \"b\"]`\n","FAILED -- Test: oracle db application owners: DBSNMP should be in \"a\" and \"b\"\nMessage: expected `DBSNMP` to be in the list: `[\"a\", \"b\"]`\n","FAILED -- Test: oracle db application owners: GSMADMIN_INTERNAL should be in \"a\" and \"b\"\nMessage: expected `GSMADMIN_INTERNAL` to be in the list: `[\"a\", \"b\"]`\n","FAILED -- Test: oracle db application owners: OJVMSYS should be in \"a\" and \"b\"\nMessage: expected `OJVMSYS` to be in the list: `[\"a\", \"b\"]`\n","FAILED -- Test: oracle db application owners: ORDSYS should be in \"a\" and \"b\"\nMessage: expected `ORDSYS` to be in the list: `[\"a\", \"b\"]`\n","FAILED -- Test: oracle db application own